4. If typecheck passes, commit with: `git add src/app/(customer)/ src/components/customer/ src/app/scan/ && git commit -m "feat: add customer portal (layout, dashboard, loyalty cards) and QR scan landing"`
5. If typecheck fails, fix the errors and try again.

